item.title: {release}my resent models i made on my free time
item.dc:creator: @JKOK JKOK
item.description:
@JKOK wrote:

[quote=“Cole1497, post:10, topic:381122”][quote author=rip4d link=topic=476939.msg3489578#msg3489578 date=1296851740]

This is the first time I’ve ever seen someone render their model with the toon effect.
It really ruins the purpose of rendering. It would have been better quality getting a camcorder and taking a picture off of your monitor. The models are nice for a first. Could you please post a wireframe?
[/quote]I always have at least 1 toon render when I show my models ._.

These models are ok. The cannon doesn’t need the massive poly-overkill though, the same thing could’ve been done with a LOT less polygons (and the cannonballs don’t need to be overdone either).

The needle could use a lot of work. I realize its a 5 minute model and all, but at least make it look like it would work

And when was the last model you posted? o.O

Topic: What is that thing at the top of the first model? It’s got squiggly lines on it.[/quote]
it was a area thet had “cannon V 2011” on it but it made the lketters small when i used the material but it was too round to add the traced immage of it since i did mesh smoothing or something X4 making it that shape but added other effects (also making it poly mega overkill but i still like it i acually might remove that when i feel like editting it :S[quote=“amy_webb, post:14, topic:381122”]Maybe if you make the pushy thinggy more longer maybe something like this?

Needle.jpg800×600

Because your liquid won’t go anywhere the way it is.[/quote]
that is acually a good point but i was just bored at the time so i made these from nowhere altho im not a “master” of it but i still like to fiddle around with it on my free time
@ all others: i still like what u sayed and i will try to make my models better in the future but i need to do more effort since i saw your guy’s\girl’s (what ever gender you are) are alot more effort then this so thanks for your thoughts
i might close this is u people want me to im just glad to see you people gave me advice and cc and some things that encourage me to do harder so anyways tyvm
